title: Under California Stars (1948) Roy Rogers | Color Western

sources.title: Under California Stars (1948) Roy Rogers | Color Western
sources.description:
Rancher Roy and his boys track down a gang who have stolen Trigger and are holding him for ransom.

Director: William Witney
Writers: Paul Gangelin, Sloan Nibley 
Stars: Roy Rogers, Trigger, Jane Frazee  
Genres: Classics, Western
